#Total Purchase

#A customer in a store is purchasing 5 items. Write a
#program that  asks for the price of each item, then
#displays the subtotal of the sale, the amount of sales tax,
#and the total.
#assume the sales tax is 7%

item1 = float(input(">"))
item2 = float(input(">"))
item3 = float(input(">"))
item4 = float(input(">"))
item5 = float(input(">"))

subtotal = item1 + item2 + item3 + item4 + item5

tax = (subtotal * 7) // 100

total = subtotal - tax

print("Subtotal {} \nTax {} \nTotal {}".format(subtotal,tax,total))
